platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Never leave money on the table

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Ebates is a fantastically easy way to earn cash-back discounts at hundreds of online stores that youre probably shopping at already. Just pick your favourite stores, and the rebates are activated whether or not you take advantage of the hot deals on tap. We love watching the savings add up and receiving a nice big cheque every few months. It almost feels like getting paid to shop.
